      "content": "\"fundamentally sound\" lol that's a pretty strong way to put it. i guess im wondering if the climate benefits are actually a proven thing or if planners just use that as a justification to pass it. like, is there any data that shows it's a real solution vs just being a way to fund the MTA?",
